# Great Job! 🎉

#### So far, you can:

* #### Identify how sequencing is introduced and developed in Music Lab
* #### Identify how students apply sequencing in creative coding tasks
* #### Support students in recognizing how the order of code affects musical output

## Up Next

#### In the next section of this professional learning module, you will:
* #### Describe how loops reduce repetition and create musical structure
* #### Learn how to guide students in identifying and applying patterns using repeat blocks
* #### Learn how to support student reasoning about loop timing and layering

___

